articles.author: Sarah Shamim
articles.title: Does Musk’s daily $1m giveaway constitute election interference? - Al Jazeera English
articles.description: Elon Musk is giving money to registered voters who sign a petition created by his pro-Trump America PAC.
articles.content: Billionaire Elon Musk has pledged to award $1m every day until election day in the United States on November 5 to randomly selected registered voters who sign a petition to support the constitution l… [+7512 chars]
